          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Preventing Gang Violence Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill establishes the Community-Based Violence Prevention Grants Program. The Department of Justice may award competitive grants to regional gang task forces to reduce and prevent violence committed by and against youths.</p>]]></text>
